	<description><![CDATA[ <div style="color:#FFFFFF; background:#056F79; border:1px solid #B0DFFF; padding:10px;margin:10px; border-radius: 4px;">
		<div><a href="http://www.techlineinfo.com" target="_blank" style="color:#FFFFFF;"><h2>Techlineinfo Responsive Social Share</h2> </a><br />A Fully responsive Beautiful Responsive Social Share buttons for your website, which adjust automatically with any type of Containers and devices.</div>
(Please post your comments, Feature Requests, bug reports here : <a href="http://www.techlineinfo.com/contact" target="_blank" style="color:#FFFFFF;">Click Here - Contact Us</a> )
